oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Commencement program, 1912
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A program from Middle Tennessee State Normal School's first commencement ceremony. Image one is the cover of the program which includes time, date, and location of the ceremony. Image two is the inside of the program; it includes the order of the ceremony and the class roll. Image three is the envelope that contained this donated item. The envelope is postmarked June 15, 1962 and shows donor and recipient.
